THIS APP HAS SOME INTERACTIVE MOMENTS 

 WHEN THE LIGHT TO THE RIGHT OF THE COMMAND BOARD COME ON 

 IT WILL BE ENABLED AND YOU WILL BE ABLE TO TYPE 

 USE \help TO GET HINTS ON WHAT TO DO 

 USE \rev TO SHOW THE COMMANDS AVAILABLE IN THE SECTION YOU ARE IN 

  HOPE YOU ENJOY IT! GOOD LUCK
